OL,3,CHow will the chancellor's Budget
OL,4,Cannouncements affect child benefit?
OL,6,FIncoming child changes were among the
OL,7,Fmeasures announced by the chancellor
OL,8,Fin his Spring .
OL,10,FJeremy Hunt revealed the news in a
OL,11,Fspeech to the House of Commons, which
OL,12,Falso included a 2p cut to National
OL,13,FInsurance and the complete scrapping
OL,14,Fof non-dom tax status.
OL,16,FAs ever the announcements have sparked
OL,17,Fmuch debate around how beneficial they
OL,18,Fwill be in reality and who they will
OL,19,Fdirectly help.
