OL,3,CHow will the chancellor's Budget
OL,4,Cannouncements affect child benefit?
OL,6,FSo, what exactly is child benefit -
OL,7,Fand how is it being affected by the
OL,8,Fchancellor's announcement? ITV News
OL,9,Fexplains.
OL,11,FWhat is child benefit?
OL,13,FChild benefit is a monthly payment
OL,14,Ffrom the government which contributes
OL,15,Ftowards the costs involved in raising
OL,16,Fa child.
OL,18,FWho does it apply to?
OL,20,FChild benefit can be applied for by
OL,21,Fpeople raising a child who is:
