OL,3,CHow will the chancellor's Budget
OL,4,Cannouncements affect child benefit?
OL,6,FOnly one person can get the benefit
OL,7,Fper child, but there is no limit to
OL,8,Fhow many children an individual can
OL,9,Fclaim for.
OL,11,FFurther information of eligibility
OL,12,Fcriteria can be found .
OL,14,FWhen can you apply for it?
OL,16,FClaims for child benefit can be made
OL,17,Fas soon as the birth has been
OL,18,Fregistered or a child has come to live
OL,19,Fwith you (e.g. fostering or adoption).
