OL,3,CHow will the chancellor's Budget
OL,4,Cannouncements affect child benefit?
OL,6,FThe process itself can take up to 16
OL,7,Fweeks to be completed and can only be
OL,8,Fbackdated by three months.
OL,10,FChild benefit claims require a CH2
OL,11,Fform to be completed and sent to the
OL,12,Fchild benefit office. This can be done
OL,13,Feither online or by sending it
OL,14,Fdirectly to the address mentioned on
OL,15,Fthe form.
