OL,3,CHow will the chancellor's Budget
OL,4,Cannouncements affect child benefit?
OL,6,FWhat changes have the government
OL,7,Fannounced?
OL,9,FThe threshold at which the high income
OL,10,Fchild benefit rate starts to be
OL,11,Fcharged will increase from #50,000 to
OL,12,F#60,000, from next month, the
OL,13,Fchancellor has announced.
OL,15,FCurrently, the charge is triggered
OL,16,Fwhen one parent in a household
OL,17,Fclaiming child benefit has taxable
OL,18,Fincome of #50,000 or more.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/9
