OL,3,CHow will the chancellor's Budget
OL,4,Cannouncements affect child benefit?
OL,6,FBut the threshold has been criticised
OL,7,Fas unfairly weighted towards single
OL,8,Fparents, as it is based on the income
OL,9,Fof the highest earner.
OL,11,FAdditionally, the rate at which the
OL,12,Ffee is charged will also be halved
OL,13,Ffrom 1% of the child benefit payment
OL,14,Ffor every additional #100 earned above
OL,15,Fthe threshold, to 1% for every #200.
OL,17,FAs a result, child benefit will not be
OL,18,Fwithdrawn in full until a parent is
OL,19,Fearning #80,000 or more.
OL,21,FWill the changes make a difference?
