OL,3,CHow will the chancellor's Budget
OL,4,Cannouncements affect child benefit?
OL,6,F"Chief among these is the high income
OL,7,Fchild benefit charge and it's welcome
OL,8,Fnews that the Chancellor has decided
OL,9,Fto recognise the unfairness of the
OL,10,Fcurrent system."
OL,12,FHe added: "Child benefit can be worth
OL,13,Fthousands of pounds a year to some
OL,14,Ffamilies and today's move could make a
OL,15,Freal difference in those household
OL,16,Fwhere budget are tight after two years
OL,17,Fof rising prices."
